### Задание 5.3 — userTask3: DML команды в БД market, пароль qwerty

```sql
CREATE USER 'userTask3'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'qwerty';
GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE ON market.* TO 'userTask3'@'localhost';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

-- Проверка:
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'userTask3'@'localhost';
```

